biotools.summary:
De-identified publicly available database of chest radiographs with free-text reports.

If you use the MIMIC-CXR Database in your work, please cite the following publication:.

MIMIC-CXR: A large publicly available database of labeled chest radiographs. Johnson AEW, Pollard TJ, Berkowitz S, Greenbaum NR, Lungren MP, Deng C-Y, Mark RG, Horng S. arXiv.. Available from: https://arxiv.org
